data.description: 5 Bedroom (or 4 Bedroom + Office) Beautifully renovated home in the highly sought-after Sungate! You will absolutely love all this home and neighborhood offers. Cooking comes easy in the Chef's Kitchen with granite, stainless & upgraded cabinetry that opens to the breakfast nook & family room with fireplace. Large Formal Living Room and Formal Dining Room are found on the front of the home looking out on the treed lot. First first-floor primary suite features a walk-in closet and private bath with double sinks. The downstairs office with a closet could easily be used as a 5th bedroom. Three large bedrooms upstairs with walk-in closets.  Flexible spaces throughout this home make it easy to envision living here - living rooms that work well as media or game rooms. The cozy front porch and large backyard decks are perfect for outdoor living. You will also find great storage throughout, built-in linen closets, a powder bath for guests, a mudroom area near the laundry, and walkout storage easily accessible from the second floor. Don’t miss the large inside storage area currently used as a playroom. And this Fall you can open the windows, turn on the attic fan, and enjoy the cool air. This beautiful neighborhood is conveniently located in midtown Tulsa near shopping and activities with a neighborhood pool, park & tennis courts just around the corner.
